|WKBSyntax: |YKBswitch|WKB, |YKBswitch <character>|WKB
|WKO===========

|YKOUse |YKBswitch|YKO to list the other characters on your account that can
be selected from your current connection. Use |YKBswitch <character>|YKO to
move to one of those characters without disconnecting.

Switching preserves your connection and parks your current body in the
linkdead room. Inventory and equipment stay with each character's body, so
switching does not move gear between characters.

Parked characters idle out normally after roughly 45 to 60 minutes.

You cannot switch while in combat. The same attack-quit cooldown that blocks
quitting after combat also blocks switching.

Aliases, triggers, highlights, chat history, and scrollback in your client
persist because they are scoped to the same server and port.
